ids_alerts.rule_msg: ET INFO DNS Query to a *.ngrok domain (ngrok.io)
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert dns $HOME_NET any -> any any (msg:"ET INFO DNS Query to a *.ngrok domain (ngrok.io)"; dns.query; content:".ngrok.io"; fast_pattern; endswith; nocase; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2022642; rev:7; metadata:created_at 2016_03_23, deployment Perimeter, confidence Medium, signature_severity Informational, updated_at 2023_04_28;)

ids_alerts.rule_msg: APP-DETECT Apple Messages push.apple.com DNS TXT request attempt
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert udp $HOME_NET any -> any 53 ( msg:"APP-DETECT Apple Messages push.apple.com DNS TXT request attempt"; flow:to_server; byte_test:1,!&,0xF8,2; content:"|04|push|05|apple|03|com|00 00 10 00 01|",fast_pattern,nocase; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:dns; reference:url,www.apple.com/osx/apps/all.html#messages; classtype:policy-violation; sid:25080; rev:2; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert tcp $EXTERNAL_NET $FILE_DATA_PORTS -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER Remote non-JavaScript file found in script tag src attribute"; flow:to_client,established; file_data; content:"<script"; content:"src=",within 30; isdataat:100,relative; content:!"|2E|js",within 100; service:ftp-data, http, imap, pop3; reference:cve,2014-6345; reference:url,technet.microsoft.com/en-us/security/bulletin/MS14-065; classtype:policy-violation; sid:32481; rev:3; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: PROTOCOL-DNS SPOOF query response with TTL of 1 min. and no authority
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert udp $EXTERNAL_NET 53 -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"PROTOCOL-DNS SPOOF query response with TTL of 1 min. and no authority"; flow:to_client; content:"|81 80|",depth 4,offset 2,fast_pattern; byte_test:2,>,0,0,relative,big; byte_test:2,>,0,2,relative,big; content:"|00 00 00 00|",within 4,distance 4; content:"|C0 0C 00 01 00 01|",distance 0; byte_test:4,<,61,0,relative,big; byte_test:4,>,0,0,relative,big; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop,ruleset community; service:dns; classtype:bad-unknown; sid:254; rev:16; )

ids_alerts.rule_msg: (http_inspect) HTTP Content-Length message body was truncated
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert ( gid:119; sid:260; rev:1; msg:"(http_inspect) HTTP Content-Length message body was truncated"; metadata: rule-type preproc; classtype:unknown; )
